---
title: Beef Patty Melts with Sweet Potato Wedges
description: If you haven't tried this iconic diner classic, tonight's the night! Think a burger, but if that burger was also a grilled cheese with caramelized onions and Dijon mustard, and served with spiced sweet potato wedges. You've probably already started cooking haven't you?
